item.title: going to ETJ training
item.description: 09:31 Sunday 31 May 2015 JST This is my first time to attend any of David Paul’s workshops (or is it Paul David?), and there’s another next week or so. My train is 20 minutes late, but I’m on time because I gave myself some time.
